{"word":"H6879 - צָרַע - tsâraʻ - tsaw-rah' - Leper","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צָרַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>tsâraʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-rah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Leper"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - குஷ்டரோகியாயிரு, குஷ்டரோகி, வெண்குஷ்டம், குஷ்டரோகியாகு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be diseased in the skin, to be leprous"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to be a leper"},{"paragraph":"b) (Pual) to have leprosy"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>scourge</i>, that is, (intransitively and figuratively) to <i>be stricken with leprosy: - </i>leper, leprous."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6871 - צְרוּעָה - Tsᵉrûwʻâh - tser-oo-aw'/6871\">H6871</a>, <a href=\"#/H6879 - צָרַע - tsâraʻ - tsaw-rah'/6879\">H6879</a>, <a href=\"#/H6880 - צִרְעָה - tsirʻâh - tsir-aw'/6880\">H6880</a>, <a href=\"#/H6881 - צׇרְעָה - Tsorʻâh - tsor-aw'/6881\">H6881</a>, <a href=\"#/H6882 - צׇרְעִי - Tsorʻîy - tsor-ee'/6882\">H6882</a>, <a href=\"#/H6883 - צָרַעַת - tsâraʻath - tsaw-rah'-ath/6883\">H6883</a>"}]}